| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4763 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 35cf0e4d-ee59-5069-9a03-e7d7382be41c"
